{"tid":974102,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"諗緊買窗口式定分體式冷氣","createTime":"2019-01-08T15:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T05:34:36.000Z","uid":87578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d5f70c681b8c5c0ea15f28867e74e79dfe04aaf1","tid":974102,"uid":87578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"客廳部冷氣都用咗成10年<br />\n今個暑假發覺佢完全唔夠做<br />\n拖到而家終於換<br />\n要吹客廳同埋我間房<br />\n200-250呎左右<br />\n諗住買2匹<br />\n夏天高峯期試過連續開24個鐘<br />\n由我起身過一陣去到第二朝屋企人醒<br />\n平均應該每日18個鐘咁上下<br />\n唔知有冇需要變頻<br />\n想要有冷暖嘅<br />\n預擺喺窗台位<br />\n咁多位巴打有無推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以捱到10年<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f643ba729dbbba16529fa705c54ccb8399fe1118","tid":974102,"uid":6378,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"用過分體唔會用返窗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff47a8802fa77e6db7561287bf4760b04d27f02","tid":974102,"uid":33878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"分體維修麻煩"},{"pid":"0236a6d078cecdc773b111a61de48cfe47b91438","tid":974102,"uid":87578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f643ba729dbbba16529fa705c54ccb8399fe1118","tid":974102,"uid":6378,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"用過分體唔會用返窗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:32:23.000Z","msg":"何解呢？<br />\n因為靜啲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我裝嘅話9成會擺喺窗台位<br />\n我最擔心其實係夠唔夠位擺<br />\n偏偏今日上嚟睇位嗰個師傅又無同我講佢度到個窗台幾大<br />\n我又search唔到<br />\n淨係話要420mm高嗰啲，因為唔可以凸出去<br />\n但係佢推個部又長過個窗台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a97ba0f2da1ff71351d28f69addf12c41b8e9c","tid":974102,"uid":87578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aff47a8802fa77e6db7561287bf4760b04d27f02","tid":974102,"uid":33878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"分體維修麻煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:32:59.000Z","msg":"咁如果窗口式嘅話巴打有冇推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2154de88e49574652db380389db1af3b6c751e41","tid":974102,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:35:01.000Z","msg":"半年前買左分體式冷氣<br />\n靜撚到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c89fd9e5aa1abb3783493b243349da3f2ad8a67","tid":974102,"uid":828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"冷暖就分體啦"},{"pid":"dc40ffc240e477db8577aa312a0409dc8b35c72b","tid":974102,"uid":87578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2154de88e49574652db380389db1af3b6c751e41","tid":974102,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:35:01.000Z","msg":"半年前買左分體式冷氣<br />\n靜撚到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:51:18.000Z","msg":"巴打買咗邊部<br />\n連安裝用咗幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屋企個設計同佢差唔多<br />\n諗緊可唔可以好似佢左邊個部咁凸出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d9f62e66adbb02ceffe7c33d7dddb233e13635","tid":974102,"uid":87578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c89fd9e5aa1abb3783493b243349da3f2ad8a67","tid":974102,"uid":828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"冷暖就分體啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T16:52:24.000Z","msg":"點解咁講<img sr