r />\n由我起身過一陣去到第二朝屋企人醒<br />\n平均應該每日18個鐘咁上下<br />\n唔知有冇需要變頻<br />\n想要有冷暖嘅<br />\n預擺喺窗台位<br />\n咁多位巴打有無推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以捱到10年<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"我幾年前買過分體 一開得耐 或太長就好易壞 <br />\n維修左一次用左3000幾蚊 <br />\n隔左一年又壞<br />\n<br />\n利申 我都係用翻窗口算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T17:28:27.000Z","msg":"巴打係買咗邊款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲人話師傅嘅手勢都好重要<br />\n我夏天嚟講應該都算開得幾耐下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你用咗幾年有冇話分體式有咩好過窗口式咁樣<br />\n依家用返窗口式又係用緊邊部<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T18:22:04.000Z","msg":"個時個師傳得出既結論係 散唔到熱所以搞到個分體機既電子板壞左 <br />\n<br />\n依家用左幾年 都幾靜 又夠涼既係 Hitachi"},{"pid":"de58acd58abee71a27683427a63c55800fecc796","tid":974102,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7475782a0458a8e8971d5684bdd57907458d4f9","tid":974102,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ce63f80d4aa9e6b15a5780797e7fe16a0adcda9","tid":974102,"uid":186755,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T01:50:38.000Z","msg":"買冷氣真係唔好買冷暖<br />\n寧願買返多部暖爐好過<br />\n以前做冷氣,D師傅/老細都叫人唔好晒錢買冷暖<br />\n冷氣機開暖氣好晒電<br />\n<br />\n利申:做左十幾年既老師父係咁講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:08:55.000Z","msg":"變頻應該唔會 太哂電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為唔會下下 full load 吹暖 除非你開到好大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T18:38:04.000Z","msg":"我而家廳部冷暖變頻<br />\n冬天凍嗰排開暖氣，都開得幾大下<br />\n但電費都無明顯變多喎"},{"pid":"bdb8f38c938148f840c52f1870eec0d78313032f","tid":974102,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fd2de8d47c2341ba03df77ec96dff07043d3553","tid":974102,"uid":64401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"我想問窗口式呢加個電費係咪都係比較貴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:33:16.000Z","msg":"仲要睇係咪變頻/雪種型號"},{"pid":"bba4738f76205a50fa9994f9269e55b6412cfb6d","tid":974102,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:11:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">窗口</span>"},{"pid":"ef112fb4457defb9b1eea69f218b6eb8eb363729","tid":974102,"uid":6378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"如果係裝分體<br />\n420: 日立/大金 二揀一<br />\n標準：大金<br />\n<br />\n其他基本唔洗諗 除非你個位裝唔落<br />\n想平 大陸格力<br />\n<br />\n不過 香港裝冷氣極之拿西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n裝分體就好似賭大細咁<br />\n我未見過中港台日會咁裝法"},{"pid":"192567f47996250ebba58a740595eba11861f632","tid":974102,"uid":6378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef112fb4457defb9b1eea69f218b6eb8eb363729","tid":974102,"uid":6378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"如果係裝分體<br />\n420: 日立/大金 二揀一<br />\n標準：大金<br />\n<br />\n其他基本唔洗諗 除非你個位裝唔落<br />\n想平 大陸格力<br />\n<br />\n不過 香港裝冷氣極之拿西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n裝分體就好似賭大細咁<br />\n我未見過中港台日會咁裝法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:50:24.000Z","msg":"係 中澳台日 打錯字"}]}